overview: "Eurosolvent" - A free DVD bootleg from the fans for the fans. Not for sale. 100% free and fully downloadable. Recorded live at Diesel Club, Budapest, August 19, 2010.  To all those who have asked about a DVD companion piece to the newest Skinny Puppy live album "Bootlegged, Broke and In Solvent Seas," this is the answer.
title: Skinny Puppy: Eurosolvent
